Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:27.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:43.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いったい何が正解なんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}タイムラインに咲き乱れるFAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:52.05,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絶望や歓喜なんて  駆け抜けるだけのMirage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溢れるインフォメーション  揺らいでいるノンフィクション
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赤い冷静  青い情熱  曖昧な審判（ジャッジ）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見透かしちゃうジーザス飼い馴らし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無関心ヴィーナス気取ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷走幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:10.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溺れていたいんでしょ  妄想はいつだって蜜の味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:16.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃ物足んないなら…「本能」（はだ）を曝せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:19.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さぁ、Naked  Dive！感情を放って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:22.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確かめろ君のREALを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう、Naked  Dive！衝動のMyself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求め続ければいいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  無我夢中で叫べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  限界はないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  その真理（こたえ）の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.34,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  拓けNew  world！
Comment: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:14.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————OPCN————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:27.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:43.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}究竟何為正解？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在時間線上爭奇鬥豔的虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:52.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕望和歡喜  只不過是穿插而過的幻景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滿溢而出的資訊  搖搖欲墜的認知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紅色代表冷靜  藍色代表熱情  這曖昧不清的判定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掌控洞悉一切的耶穌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假冒冰冷美豔的維納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷茫幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:10.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要沉溺於其中吧  妄想無論何時都如蜜之味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:16.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若是還不夠的話…那就把「本能」都展現出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:19.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧  Naked  Dive！  將感情釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:22.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去確定屬於你的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯  Naked  Dive！  不斷追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}屬於自己內心的那份衝動不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  盡情地呼喊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  沒有任何界限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  邁向那片真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  開拓新的世界！
Comment: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:10.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,————————EDJP————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:16.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,新しいわたしで どんなときも向き合いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:19.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなで笑顔になれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:32.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,好きなことができてたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:37.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,一方通行じゃやっぱ ものたりないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:40.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かに伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,嬉しすぎると泣けちゃうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しすぎると笑っちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:50.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな毎日にトクンてきてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:53.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぼんやりふくらんだ夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:56.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとすぐ破裂しちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:59.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,悔しかったあの日のPain　(No need!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:02.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,掴むべきは　これからのShine　(Yes!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:04.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　(Yes!)　叶えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:06.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぜったいにできるって！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:08.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,鳥が空とぶように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:12.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,星が夜をかざるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,当たり前みたいに いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:17.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かに見てもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:19.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:25.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ白なこころで迎えた朝は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:25.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ハツラツだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.24,0:23:28.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}だから元気をおくろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(200,0)}All right!　変わってく景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:33.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}Always!　一緒にみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}All right!　もちろん全力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(0,200)}Always!　純真で　It's all right!
Comment: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:10.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————EDCN————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:16.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想无时无刻以全新的自己面对一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:19.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起冁然而笑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:32.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对于爱不释手的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:37.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,光是独享 果然是远远不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想要将其分享给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:43.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,喜极而泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,悲中苦笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:50.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,每一天都令人期待不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:53.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不明不白膨胀的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会马上破灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:59.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔过去的痛苦 （没必要！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,该牢牢握住的是未来的曙光 （Yes!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:04.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 （Yes!） 一定能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:06.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,必定会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如同翱翔于天际的小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:12.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛点缀于夜空的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:14.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时都理所当然地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:17.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想要让别人也一起欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:19.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:25.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,以纯白内心所迎接的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:25.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么令人精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:28.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}所以  想将活力赠于你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:31.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(200,0)}All  right!  不断变化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:34.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}Always!  想要与你一起观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:36.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}All  right!  当然会全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(0,200)}Always!  维持纯真便行了!
Comment: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:11.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————Text————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,phantom究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还存在很多不解之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.97,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(583.2,671.4)\fad(300,0)}名词
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.97,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1327.2,666.6)\fad(300,0)}1.幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.97,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(758.4,755.4)\fad(300,0)}2.幽灵  鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们认为其来源的一种就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类所想象出的幻影的实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有被人类制造出来的phantom啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说phantom的存在和人类的潜在意识
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及语言系统有着莫大的关联
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你之前所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣格的集体潜意识也有关联吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:27.25,English,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(897.6,952.5)}collective  unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在荣格心理学中  有个原型理论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:31.51,English,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1186.4,952.5)}archetype
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是谁  内心都有着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指引方向的智慧老人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为异性的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及被压抑的自身另一面等等的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西会变成phantom吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是人类所想象出的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能变成phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说以及童话也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定有一天白雪公主或者灰姑娘这种也会变成phantom出现咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浦岛太郎和开花爷爷也有可能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见一见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说是没有版权的  所以没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神振之力  phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于托托天伦中显其虚像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩的团队配合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈  爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久瑠美  看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸  笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时至七月中旬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉  我们E队取得了消灭phantom的最好成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就快要暑假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一直忙得要死  我都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合宿是要去海边吧  海边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和父母商量了下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们允许我去合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在和你父母相处得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  最近他们比以前更会考虑我的感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸  你知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是通讯设备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿赖耶识社服务器专用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通讯设备？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这个的话  是无法连接阿赖耶识社的服务器的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这哪弄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是之前去阿赖耶识社废弃工厂的时候捡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被回收留在那了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了…水无濑学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是学姐的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我们拍张合影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备  茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去向大家炫耀炫耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸真受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人会给我写信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了  真是不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明也表现很出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能更受欢迎点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来表扬你吧  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都在朝着好的方向发展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为是这样的  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁城镇的特异能力者被phantom袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  好像有其他学校的学生也被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是phantom吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我们有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击特异能力者的人就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天  其他学校的特异能力者被来历不明的phantom袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个phantom被称为「enigma」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特征和来历均不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现阶段知道的就只有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到袭击的特异能力者  其能力会被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夺走是指  能力会转移到enigma身上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然phantom对策局已亲自展开调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但请各位也要充分保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上下学尽量多人同行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算遇到也不要战斗  快点逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.94,TIPS1,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦见到enigma请立即联络phantom对策局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击特异能力者的phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是出现了奇怪的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma是什么样的熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.03,TIPS1,NTP,0,0,0,,gma和熊（kuma）发音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma不是熊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希腊语中「谜」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第二次世界大战中曾被用作密码机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及管弦乐曲的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来历不明这点很怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,phantom对策局和阿赖耶识社竟然都没有情报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的合宿要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担心的居然是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  小糸  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈和久瑠美你们留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥姐姐  小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说话吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海滩天使的学姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  是enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙会用嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快退后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现身  克苏鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克苏鲁~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神振之力  phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于托托天伦中显其虚像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  为什么自己消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是封印完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是我们的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海滩天使的学姐们所住的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿赖耶识社的研究所附属医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没受多大的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却失去了特异能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人们的脑机能发生变化的根本原因就是阿赖耶识社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在phantom和特异能力的研究方面是世界第一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能指望他们的技术了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她们能早点康复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夺走的能力没有恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说enigma可能还尚在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不知道有没有成功封印它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:19.66,TIPS1,NTP,0,0,0,,医院内请保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是它出现  就再把它干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可自那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma并没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们也进入了暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  又在弄那个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点就能修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去学校和大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶尔也到舞学姐她们那去玩玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么成天只缠着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是一条家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是晴彦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸联系不上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是一如既往那么忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦你已经放暑假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是高中生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪个学校念书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是突然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都牵挂着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你结婚的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很早之前就分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实很早就想联系你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一想到你肯定不会原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就失去了联系的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你能来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  突然打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要努力学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:12:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又和曾抛弃我的妈妈一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我再睡一会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了你喜欢的纳豆天妇罗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那起来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样过了一周
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得有些奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然回来  陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人真的是晴彦你的妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想说是phantom伪装的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候的事她知道的一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且身体看上去也是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能陪我去买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向日葵的种子我可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该给我死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hima  hima  hima
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片向日葵田里的向日葵都是本大爷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的向日葵是属于土地所有者的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴wari  闭嘴wari  闭嘴wari
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙  这家伙的弱点是太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hima…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是向日葵  所以只能面向太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,himagi…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员移动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  你们这些卑鄙小人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周都没露面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎很享受和妈妈在一起的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也两个人一起去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟一直在等着他妈妈回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能懂他想要一直待在妈妈身边的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此  也不能疏远了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  你不知不觉间怎么就变成我们队的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈妈是个怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想  就是那个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是晴彦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我拿一半吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是他妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且看起来好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很微弱  但感觉到有可疑的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是phantom？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  是至今为止从没感觉到过的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先联系姬野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再亲自去会会她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴  竟然来了这么多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来  快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次买多点食材真是买对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是川神舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子一直以来受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  我才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是和泉玲奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢吃得多的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是水无濑小糸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜品我也准备了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是熊枕久瑠美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  大家快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的气息怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我遇到过的家族phantom也不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有那么多的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的儿子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对大家很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和妈妈一起生活真是太好了呢  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也很替你开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还有些不习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  她们之中有晴彦你喜欢的女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许将来她们之中会有人成为我的儿媳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想现在就了解一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家和我的儿子关系都很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和他在一起生活过一周啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对我说过「我们这个团队就是你的归宿」这类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  很多地方都对我很照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是  晴彦哥哥总是会给予我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好接纳儿媳的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都欢迎你们任何一个人成为我的儿媳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说谈这事还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气氛是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家完全被牵着鼻子走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(343.2,1020)}饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  接个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真羡慕啊  有那样的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川神同学  听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人向警方申请了一条妈妈的搜寻请求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提出申请的就是她现在的结婚对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在大约一周前  她突然变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随后就下落不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下落不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有给一条的家里打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但联系不上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  enigma还有那种能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  那么说她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个妈妈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  这家伙不是你的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才老师打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说enigma有侵占人类意识的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本打算再观察下情况的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来该下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是侵占了人类的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得会感觉到奇怪的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你的能力非常感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自由地召唤phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能潜入他人的意识和记忆之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你用得太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是用得好的话  这可是能成为最强的能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个能力  我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈  小糸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个力量给人类太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来好好利用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快送他去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露  怎么连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
